name: FINAL ATTACK - Legitimate Threat CD (FNR001)
description: Final Attack's first full length CD. Fast and heavy hardcore influenced by bands like Cro Mags, Leeway, Madball, Negative Approach, Minor threat and the likes. For fans of bands mentioned above. In the words of their own.."Just straight up pissed off hardcore the way we want it to be. " Check out one of their new song from the upcoming CDEP titled "LENGTH OF TIME" at FINAL ATTACK THEIR UPCOMING CDEP IS AVAILABLE FOR PRE-ORDER HERE. FIRSNOTE RECORDS

FIRSNOTE RECORDS

name: BRAVE HEART - Wake Up Call CD PRE-ORDER (FNR003)
description: BRAVE HEART's first ever full length will be out next month. This is the PRE-ORDER. Melodic hard hitting passionate full of heart - that's pretty much sums up about their upcoming full length. Representing their Straight Edge belief, this is what they're offering you. JAKARTA CITY STRAIGHT EDGE IS ON THE MOVE. Will start shipping hopefully on the 3rd week of February, that is if there is no more delay from the pressing plant. BRAVE HEART FIRSNOTE RECORDS
